reviewText: not what you would expect from the cover but it was pretty decent it got the job done if you know what I mean
I have bought 8 vides by critical mass and will not buy another. The story is good but the anime is flat and looks like it comes from the 70's
the content was not well thought out did not have much of a plot was not interesting again you get what you pay for.
To me, the animation was not very good. I guess my expectations were too high. I would not recommend this.

This was another great DVD of this genre. I'm not exactly sure what I can and cannot write regarding this kind of stuff seeing as how it's for adults and this is adult material so adult language should be fine.
